 VGM Example E05
 Converting geometry from AGDD to Root
 --------------------------------------
 
 Source: The AGDD test file for solids
         Main program agdd2root.cxx
         
 1. The provided installation script (E05/install.sh)
    will install rootgeom.cxx main program:
    ./install.sh
    
    This step is not necessary if you installed all examples
    at once from up directory.
  
 2. Your environment for VGM has to be set first, see doc/INSTALL)
    
 3. Run example
    ./agdd2root
 
 4. Open and view the generated Root file 
    root
    root [0] new TGeoManager("AGDD test", "AGDD test for solids");
    root [1] gGeoManager->Import("geometry.root");
    root [2] gGeoManager->GetTopVolume()->Draw();

                
